  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Day 53 Lesson 1&nbsp;</p><p>Before starting this lesson, please download this PDF file with our grammar introduction: <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/thinkific/file_uploads/259518/attachments/d06/b76/7a8/Day_53_Lesson_1_-_Grammar_Explanation.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Day 53 Lesson 1 - Grammar Explanation.pdf</a></p><p><ruby>前&nbsp;<rt>まえ</rt></ruby>もって<ruby>準備<rt>じゅんび</rt></ruby>しておくことを <ruby>話<rt>はな</rt></ruby>す / <ruby>次回<rt>じかい</rt></ruby>の <ruby>使用<rt>しよう</rt></ruby>のための <ruby>後片付&nbsp;<rt>あとかたづ</rt></ruby>けについて <ruby>話<rt>はな</rt></ruby>す = Talking about things done in advance / Talking about cleaning up for the next use</p><p><ruby><b>場所</b> <rt>ばしょ</rt>&nbsp;</ruby><b>= Location:</b>&nbsp; <ruby>教室&nbsp;<rt>きょうしつ</rt>&nbsp;</ruby><ruby><ruby>（パーティーの<ruby>準備<rt>じゅんび</rt></ruby>をしている）</ruby>&nbsp;</ruby>= Classroom (preparing for a party)<br><br><ruby><b>登場人物</b><rt>とうじょうじんぶつ</rt>&nbsp;</ruby><b>= Characters:</b>&nbsp; <ruby>先生&nbsp;<rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>、リンさん <ruby>、スミスさん &nbsp; <ruby>留学生二人<rt>りゅうがくせいふたり</rt></ruby><ruby>&nbsp;</ruby></ruby>= Teacher, Lin-san, Smith-san two study abroad students</p><p><span class=\"fr-video fr-fvc fr-dvb\"><iframe src=\"https://platform.thinkific.com/videoproxy/v1/play/bs8ka6tab8ion3qpfdt0\" scrolling=\"no\" class=\"videoproxy_embed\" title=\"D53 L1 C1.mp4 - 00:47\" name=\"videoproxy_embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></span></p><p>For the new words in this video, please check the subtitles and refer to the vocabulary section.</p></div>",
